    "content_id":  "87ed04a3-ee2e-44d2-b0d5-543d67992197",
    "description":  "Use this \u0027framework\u0027 to buy loose and fitted school furniture and bleacher seating from Department for Education (DfE) approved suppliers and have it delivered and installed. ",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [

                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"who-can-buy-furniture\"\u003eWho can buy furniture\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAll educational settings.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"the-furniture-you-can-buy\"\u003eThe furniture you can buy\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe school furniture you can buy has been grouped into lots. Buy from one or more lots depending on what you need.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"lot-1---loose-furniture\"\u003eLot 1 - loose furniture:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eprimary and secondary school pupils’ chairs, stools and tables\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eteachers’ chairs and tables\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003estorage units\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003epedestal units\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003escience tables\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003etray units\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003edouble-sided bookcases\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"lot-2---fitted-furniture\"\u003eLot 2 - fitted furniture:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eworktops\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eunder bench tray units (with or without doors)\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ewall cupboards\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ewall shelving\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003epedestal units (wet and dry)\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eL-shaped teachers’ service desks\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eteachers’ service bollards\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e4 door lockers\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"lot-3---bleacher-furniture\"\u003eLot 3 - bleacher furniture:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ebleachers to seat 240 with upholstered seat and back\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eupholstered benching with back\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"when-the-framework-expires\"\u003eWhen the framework expires\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eMarch 2024.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"the-framework-id\"\u003eThe framework ID\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe ID for this framework is: 2019-041978\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"how-to-buy-school-furniture\"\u003eHow to buy school furniture\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThere are 2 ways you can buy furniture.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"buy-direct-from-suppliers-for-orders-below-2000\"\u003e1. Buy direct from suppliers for orders below £2,000\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eFor orders below £2,000, contact the supplier directly through their website and mention this framework.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003cthead\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"col\"\u003eSupplier website\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"col\"\u003eLot 1\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"col\"\u003eLot 2\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"col\"\u003eLot 3\u003c/th\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"row\"\u003e\n\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.completebusinesssolutionseducation.co.uk/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eComplete Business Solutions\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eNo\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"row\"\u003e\n\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.morleys.co.uk/pages/department-for-education-furniture-framework/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eMorleys\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"row\"\u003e \u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://pinnacle-furniture.co.uk/our-services/dfe-furniture-framework/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003ePinnacle Furniture\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eNo\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"row\"\u003e\n\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://apteriors.com/dfe-furniture-framework/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eApteriors\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eNo\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"row\"\u003e\n\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.southernsbroadstock.co.uk/dfe-portal/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eSoutherns Broadstock\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003cth scope=\"row\"\u003e\n\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.ypo.co.uk/education/dfe-furniture-framework\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eYorkshire Purchasing Organisation (YPO)\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/th\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eNo\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"run-a-mini-competition-for-orders-over-2000\"\u003e2. Run a mini-competition for orders over £2,000\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eFor orders over £2,000, you need to run a mini-competition between the suppliers that offer the goods you want.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can either:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003efollow the advice and guidance on how to \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/buying-procedures-and-procurement-law-for-schools/run-a-mini-competition\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003erun a mini-competition\u003c/a\u003e yourself\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eget advice and guidance from \u003cabbr title=\"Department for Education\"\u003eDfE\u003c/abbr\u003e on how to run a mini-competition by emailing \u003ca href=\"mailto:GetHelpBuyingForSchools@education.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eGetHelpBuyingForSchools@education.gov.uk\u003c/a\u003e with:\n    \u003cul\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003eyour name\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003ethe school name and postcode\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003ethe lot you are interested in\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003ebrief details of the products required\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003eestimated spend\u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\n  \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e",
